{"id":186946,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/10/译者-《译者》每日原文推荐-2011107/","date":"2011-10-08T01:00:31Z","modified":"2011-10-08T08:45:20Z","title":"译者 | 《译者》每日原文推荐 &#8211; 2011/10/7_","content":"<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">以下为每日原文推荐。如果你有兴趣，请参与翻译并将译文寄给</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://yyyyiiii.blogspot.com/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《译者》</span></a><span> </span><strong>(</strong></span><span><strong><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"mailto:iyizhe@gmail.com\"><span>iyizhe@gmail.com</span></a>)</span></strong></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">以便与大家共享。欢迎使用</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feedburner.google.com/fb/a/mailverify?uri=yizhe&amp;loc=en_US\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">邮件组</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">、</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://goo.gl/f1NDK\">Google Reader</a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">和推特（</span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#!/yigroup\">@yigroup</a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#!/xiaomi2020\">@xiaomi2020</a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">）跟踪我们的最新消息。</span></span><span> </span></p>\n<p><span><span> </span></span><span> </span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【时政热点】</span><span> </span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《纽约时报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.nytimes.com/2011/10/08/world/asia/calls-for-release-of-chinese-nobel-laureate-liu-xiaobo.html?_r=1&amp;partner=rss&amp;emc=rss\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">人权组织呼吁释放中国的诺贝尔奖获奖者</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“只有在强大的国际压力下，中国政府才会提前释放刘晓波。但现在没有这样的压力”</span></span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span>MSNBC</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">博客：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://behindthewall.msnbc.msn.com/_news/2011/10/07/8203118-for-chinese-winners-wife-nobel-is-no-prize\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">对于刘晓波的妻子而言，诺贝尔奖带来的不是奖励</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——自从刘晓波一年前获奖，刘霞便被软禁起来，过着孤独与压抑的日子。</span></span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《卫报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2011/oct/07/tibetan-monk-self-immolation-death\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">西藏又现</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">自焚事件：两名年轻</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">藏人周五</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">自焚，一名死亡</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“自由西藏”组织称他们是前格尔登寺喇嘛。阿坝公安局否认有人自焚。</span></span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">迈齐报系：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.mcclatchydc.com/2011/10/06/126391/after-100-years-corruption-still.html?storylink=addthis#.To5o_YSjxZM.twitter\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">一百年过去了，腐败仍是中国的大问题</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——记者以北京近郊一起官商之间的腐败案，将当前中国的腐败程度与清末做了对比</span></span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《卫报》：华西村：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2011/oct/06/huaxi-village-tower-china\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">耸立在中国之上的村庄</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——华西村的豪华酒店比伦敦任何建筑都要高，人们的地位和待遇是按与吴氏家族的关系远近来分配的。</span></span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国外人博客：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://chinabystander.wordpress.com/2011/10/07/chinas-power-shortages-set-to-persist/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国的供电短缺还会持续下去</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——南方的旱灾使水电站难以发力，内蒙的煤电虽有过剩但又鞭长莫及。</span></span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《外交学者》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://the-diplomat.com/2011/10/08/taiwan%E2%80%99s-asymmetric-china-plan/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">台湾非对称的大陆政策</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——美国拒绝售台先进</span></span><span><span>F-16</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">战机，促使台湾在军事上做出针对大陆的非对称战略。美国需要在政治、经济和军事三方面加以支持。</span></span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《时代》周刊：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.time.com/time/world/article/0,8599,2096450,00.html?xid=rss-world&amp;utm_source=feedburner&amp;utm_medium=feed&amp;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+time%2Fworld+%28TIME%3A+Top+World+Stories%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">诺贝尔奖女获奖者：今年的和平奖被三位争取自身权利的女士获得</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——介绍来自非洲的三位女获奖者：两位利比里亚人，一位也门人。</span></span><span></span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【国际外交】</span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《大西洋》月刊：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.theatlantic.com/international/archive/2011/10/is-chinas-influence-waxing-or-waning/246308/#.To8un5QNYXY.twitter\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国的影响是在上升还是在下降？</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——过去两个星期中国在国际上的影响力指标出现大幅度波动：赞比亚和缅甸对中国说不，而南非则顺从中国而拒绝了达赖。</span></span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《纽约时报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.nytimes.com/2011/10/07/world/asia/pakistan-pulls-closer-to-a-reluctant-china.html?partner=rss&amp;emc=rss\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">巴基斯坦主动靠近，中国态度勉强</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——巴基斯坦用中国来取代与美国日渐疏远的关系，但中国并不打算付出太多。</span></span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《外交学者》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://the-diplomat.com/indian-decade/2011/10/07/india-china-eye-border-plan/?utm_source=feedburner&amp;utm_medium=feed&amp;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+the-diplomat+%28The+Diplomat+RSS%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中印致力于边界规划</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——虽然双方在南海问题上关系趋紧，但有报道称他们仍然在建设性地讨论处理边界争端的新机制。</span></span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《外交学者》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://the-diplomat.com/china-power/2011/10/07/china-and-the-eurasian-union/?utm_source=feedburner&amp;utm_medium=feed&amp;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+the-diplomat+%28The+Diplomat+RSS%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国与“欧亚联盟”</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——普京为与中国争夺在中亚的战略利益，号召以前苏联加盟共和国为主成立“欧亚联盟”。中国对此态度轻蔑。</span></span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">卡内基基金会：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.carnegieendowment.org/2011/10/06/sustainable-u.s.-china-security-relationship/5qzr\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">实现可持续的美中安全关系</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——《美国的挑战》一书作者点评中美在台湾、南海和朝鲜问题上的关系，认为应该保持大方向，作出小调整</span></span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">路透社：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/10/06/us-usa-china-subsidies-idUSTRE7955GM20111006\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美国指责中印掩盖补贴项目</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——美国向世贸组织抱怨说中国有</span></span><span><span>200</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">多项政府补贴项目没有通报，要求世贸采取行动，增加中国的透明度。</span></span><span></span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【经济金融】</span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《金融时报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://blogs.ft.com/beyond-brics/2011/10/07/guest-post-chinas-disappearing-bank-deposits/#axzz1a4yoHzSZ\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国不翼而飞的一万一千亿元银行存款</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——今年七月，储户和公司从银行里提走了相当于</span></span><span><span>GDP2.5%</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">的存款。这些钱到底去了哪里？</span></span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">路透社：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://old.news.yahoo.com/s/nm/20111007/bs_nm/us_economy_china_property\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">给中国的房地产泡沫降温</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——美国人用房子来借钱，中国人用房子来储蓄。因此，即使中国房地产泡沫破裂，结果也不会象美国那么严重</span></span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span> </span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【生活百态】</span></span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">迷途老外博客：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.lostlaowai.com/blog/china-stuff/china-travel/prostitutes-and-full-immersion-learning/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">妓女与实地学习</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——老外来中国学习中文的好处就是可以实地接触生活。这位作者从妓女的揽客卡上学到了白领和发票是什么。</span></span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国见红博客：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://seeingredinchina.com/2011/10/07/everyone-in-america-has-guns-china-is-the-safest-country-in-the-world/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美国人人都有枪，中国是世界上最安全的地方</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——昨天说了外国人对中国的感受，今天说说中国人对外国的看法。</span></span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span> </span></span></p>\n<div><em>发送邮件至 yyyyiiii+subscribe@googlegroups.com 即可订阅译文；译者的音频博客已登录iTunes，到<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://itunes.apple.com/us/podcast/id453722327?ign-mpt=uo%3D4\">这里</a>即可收听往期的译者音频节目；下载更新需翻墙。</em><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/5425822223623422432-1672586552958054444?l=yyyyiiii.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" /></div>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\" method=\"POST\"> 定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a><br />\n<input maxlength=\"64\" name=\"EMAIL\" size=\"25\" type=\"text\" /></p>\n<p><input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\" /> <input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\" /> <input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\" /> </form>\n","author":1,"categories":[1],"tags":[9041,18836,8840]}